You meet or face people, characters, that sometimes you don&#39;t even know, or that leave you only a few minutes to take the photo.
Despite these circumstances, as a photographer, I always try to make my ideas come true. &quot;
This collection of portraits of current flamenco entitled &quot;Flamenco-people&quot; is exhibited in the Galería El Fotomachta, located at number 20 de la Mata street, parallel to the Alameda de Hércules, where it can be visited until the next 16 October.
